A corny joke inspired by Dan and Arin:
A teacher is talking to her students and asks:
Teacher: Okay class, what sound does a dog make?
Students: Bark! Bark!
Teacher: Good. What sound does a cat make?
Students: Meow!
Teacher: Good. Now a hard one. What sound does a seal make?
One boy raises his hand. The teacher calls on him.
Boy: Bah-da-da dada dah dah dah dah.
Badadah
The~ere used to be a graying tower alone on the sea.
